===Noun===
'''[[future]] [[perfect]] [[continuous]]'''

# {{grammar}} A tense used to express an ongoing action completed after some time in the future; in English it is formed by use of will have been (or shall have been) and a past participle.
#:Example: ''By the end of this year, I '''will have been working''' here for 10 years.''

